{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2014}} '''Mike Wozniak''' is a British comedian, writer and actor. He is best known for portraying Brian in the Channel 4 sitcom ''[[Man_Down_(TV_series)|Man Down]]'' and as a member of the team that make ''Small Scenes'' for [[BBC Radio 4]]. In 2015 he wrote a [[physical comedy]] starring [[Kim Cattrall]] and a troupe of acrobats entitled ''Ruby Robinson'' for SKY Arts. In 2016 he played the role of Josh in Alice Lowe's ''[[Prevenge]]''.
